01:52:00,23 --> 01:52:04,55
Nevertheless, Katie Scarlett, I don't like it. I shall speak to Mrs. O'Hara about it.

01:52:18,77 --> 01:52:20,90
What are you doing out of bed, Melly?

01:52:20,93 --> 01:52:24,13
