01:52:25,97 --> 01:52:28,50
Go on back upstairs. You're as weak as a newborn colt.

01:52:28,57 --> 01:52:29,84
Please, Scarlett, let me.

01:52:29,91 --> 01:52:32,21
Stop being noble. I've got enough on my hands

01:52:32,28 --> 01:52:35,18
without you making yourseIf sick so you'll never be any use.

