That won't be enough.

02:03:01,81 --> 02:03:04,00
What in heaven's name are you talking about?

02:03:04,08 --> 02:03:08,52
Well, Miss Scarlett, I seed that old no-count white-trash Wilkerson

02:03:08,55 --> 02:03:11,08
that used to be Mr. Gerald's overseer here.

02:03:11,15 --> 02:03:14,55
He's a regular Yankee now, and he was making a brag

02:03:14,82 --> 02:03:20,20
that his carpetbagger friends done run the taxes way up sky-high on Tara.

02:03:20,23 --> 02:03:21,76
But how much more have we got to pay?

